    h4 Semantic Layers
    .margin-bottom-lg
      p Each layer has 3 parts to it: background, text, and border.
      p.margin-bottom-md For example with layer 3, you have --neutral-layer-3-background, --neutral-layer-3-text, and --neutral-layer-3-border
      .flex
        .card style="background: var(--neutral-layer-1-background); border: 3px solid var(--neutral-layer-1-border);"
          span style="color: var(--neutral-layer-1-text)" = "--neutral-layer-1"
          .card style="background: var(--neutral-layer-2-background); border: 3px solid var(--neutral-layer-2-border);"
            span style="color: var(--neutral-layer-2-text)" = "--neutral-layer-2"
            .card style="background: var(--neutral-layer-3-background); border: 3px solid var(--neutral-layer-3-border);"
